{
  "stem": "6195.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, 1935, in June--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'39-- I'm sorry-- I graduated, and I was graduated in flying colors.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I was terribly, terribly happy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody was happy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we went on holidays with my mother and my sister and my brother.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my father used to stay home and come to join us on-- for the Shabbat and Sunday.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And that was for two months, we used to go.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I felt so relieved that, you know, I'll have-- I'll, I'll be able to see my friends and have a good time and read a lot.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I love reading.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so about two weeks before the war, when my father was-- has joined us on the weekend, he said, there are rumors that the Germans are surrounding Poland, far, far from-- far, far away from the borders.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But something is going on, and maybe it would be wise to come, to come home earlier.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so we came home, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] 27th of August or something like that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] on the-- one day, I got on the train.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And went-- I just had to meet some girls at the king's palace, the king's-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Wawel, in Cracow.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It's called Wawel, W-A-W-E-L.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That was the king's-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] all the kings were there when Poland was a kingdom.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it's very beautiful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we used to sort of meet there, and the Vistula River beneath, and it was very beautiful.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I took the tram.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was a lazy walker always.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And suddenly, the sirens-- we heard sirens.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the tram stopped, and we were told to get out.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
